Given:
```java
class A { void go(Object o) { System.out.println("A-Object"); } }
class B extends A {
    @Override void go(Object o) { System.out.println("B-Object"); }
    void go(String s)           { System.out.println("B-String"); }
}
```
Predict for: `A a=new B(); a.go("hi");` and `B b=new B(); b.go("hi");`

